Dialogue: 6,0:01:47.77,0:01:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 6,0:01:52.93,0:01:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 6,0:01:53.82,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 6,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for causing a stir so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:01.33,0:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just confessed my feelings to your daughter.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:05.63,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 6,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How polite.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want a reply.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:12.49,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't let it remain unsaid.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:15.71,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Remain unsaid?
Dialogue: 6,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, we're going to be late.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 6,0:02:36.22,0:02:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're keeping your distance.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine!
Dialogue: 6,0:02:39.58,0:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Okay, then.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking back at it now,
Dialogue: 6,0:02:48.18,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think that Kaname and Chisaki were acting a little strange that day.
Dialogue: 6,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But at the time,
Dialogue: 6,0:02:56.84,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my mind was filled with thoughts of our \Nupcoming hibernation, the Boatdrift Ceremony,
Dialogue: 6,0:03:01.11,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and most of all, Manaka.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I think Manaka had \Nthe same things on her mind.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:08.71,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why Manaka and I could never have caught on to those two at the time.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:10.79,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're late!
Dialogue: 6,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 6,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 6,0:03:16.17,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fact was that, in the few days that followed,
Dialogue: 6,0:03:20.00,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the world around us changed \Nat an unbelievable pace.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Day in, day out,
Dialogue: 6,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the saltflake snow continued to fall.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:30.41,0:03:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before we knew it, our village had turned completely white,
Dialogue: 6,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}like somewhere from a snowy country.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:38.77,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, the preparations for our sleep continued on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:42.07,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.23\blur0.8\c&HB5B451&\frz15.21\move(705,369,705,135,25,2235)}Closed to {\c&HB4B455&}Prep{\c&HBBBA5E&}ar{\c&HC2C27A&}e
