Dialogue: 6,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone stopped eating,
Dialogue: 6,0:03:51.86,0:03:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and their Ena got thicker and thicker.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:57.37,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At first, it was hard to imagine that we'd actually fall asleep one day,
Dialogue: 6,0:04:02.29,0:04:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{mou me no mae}but that day crept closer and closer until it was right in front of us, undeniably real.
Dialogue: 6,0:04:09.37,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{chijou ni}On the surface, the saltflake snow had only fallen once more,
Dialogue: 6,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but that summer was much colder then usual,
Dialogue: 6,0:04:16.70,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I think everyone started to work a little more seriously because of it.
Dialogue: 6,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 6,0:04:25.25,0:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,According to {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama},\N at the rate our Ena are progressing,
Dialogue: 6,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we will most likely fall into \Nour sleep on the 21st.
Dialogue: 6,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
