Dialogue: 6,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The 21st?
Dialogue: 6,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the day of the Boatdrift Ceremony!
Dialogue: 6,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So on the day of the festival,
Dialogue: 6,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be waving goodbye to \Neveryone on the surface.
Dialogue: 6,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They can all just cool off for a bit in the snow.
Dialogue: 6,0:04:47.86,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ungrateful, thick-headed jerks!
Dialogue: 6,0:04:51.27,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we're the thick ones right now, with our Ena and all.
Dialogue: 6,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,True, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.23,The Club of the Kettle,,0,0,0,,{\frz0.01\blur0.6\c&H151D20&\frx324\fry0\fscx149\fscy181\pos(651.04,673.98)}Men's Club
Dialogue: 6,0:04:59.72,0:05:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 6,0:05:00.54,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys on the surface right now might not even be there anymore when we wake up.
Dialogue: 6,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 6,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 6,0:05:14.79,0:05:15.96,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?{alt}
Dialogue: 6,0:05:20.57,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 6,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 6,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 6,0:05:28.35,0:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as usual, really.
Dialogue: 6,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be because I've been out of the ocean for so long,
Dialogue: 6,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but I haven't been affected like the others.
Dialogue: 6,0:05:36.73,0:05:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I should hold off going on any diets for a while, though.
