Dialogue: 6,0:05:52.21,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you really want?
Dialogue: 6,0:06:03.33,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept me, to have and to hold, despite my faults.
Dialogue: 6,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please accept me too.
Dialogue: 6,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and about the ceremony...
Dialogue: 6,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 6,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking there's probably no need.
Dialogue: 6,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Given our situation,
Dialogue: 6,0:06:28.65,0:06:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt my dad would attend even if I invited him.
Dialogue: 6,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 6,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you think that's exactly why we should have a proper ceremony?
Dialogue: 6,0:06:38.42,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your dad would like to see you as a bride as well.
Dialogue: 6,0:06:44.49,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's think about it.
Dialogue: 6,0:06:47.25,0:06:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have a ceremony that fits us,
Dialogue: 6,0:06:51.09,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not ready to give up yet on getting your dad's blessing.
Dialogue: 6,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Itaru{-san}.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:02.83,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This country originally had a humid, temperate climate.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:07.57,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was best known for the changes in weather that came with the seasons,
Dialogue: 6,0:07:11.75,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which were brought about by what we call the seasonal winds.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 6,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like it's time.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:20.68,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You four can go ahead.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even midday yet.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Ena's fine.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:27.38,0:07:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,These instructions came straight from Shioshishio, though.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We should respect them.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:33.36,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hibernation is thought to be a biochemical reaction
Dialogue: 6,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,brought about by a combination of environmental factors.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:41.27,0:07:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it hasn't happened for centuries, so we're not sure.
Dialogue: 6,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But {replace}Teach{Sensei}, we're fine—
Dialogue: 6,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 6,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 6,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 6,0:07:59.40,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Ena's become thicker, \Nand it needs water more often.
Dialogue: 6,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't dawdle, now.
Dialogue: 6,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 6,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dry as a bone already.
Dialogue: 6,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We really are going to sleep.
Dialogue: 6,0:08:39.55,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 6,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 6,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when we go to sleep at the same time each night,
Dialogue: 6,0:08:46.90,0:08:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we often wake up at different times, right?
Dialogue: 6,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So are we all really gonna be able to wake up at the same time?
Dialogue: 6,0:08:56.12,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}Isn't everyone going to sleep together and waking up together?
Dialogue: 6,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee.
Dialogue: 6,0:09:05.18,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After our hibernation, not only will the surface be different, but so will we.
Dialogue: 6,0:09:12.05,0:09:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time we can be sure we'll spend together is right now.
Dialogue: 6,0:09:17.81,0:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fleeting thing.
Dialogue: 6,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you guys want to do about lunch?
Dialogue: 6,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Teach{Sensei} said I should ask you just in case.
Dialogue: 6,0:09:31.57,0:09:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do have amazing timing, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 6,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna eat.
Dialogue: 6,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You'll get in trouble.
Dialogue: 6,0:09:44.54,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 6,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just gonna quietly go to sleep
Dialogue: 6,0:09:48.27,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when we don't even know \Nwhat'll happen afterward!
Dialogue: 6,0:10:00.68,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 6,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 6,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat too!
Dialogue: 6,0:10:14.58,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... I don't want all that to happen.
Dialogue: 6,0:10:19.05,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go to sleep and wake up\N to find everything has changed.
Dialogue: 6,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 6,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 6,0:10:54.03,0:10:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 6,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 6,0:11:05.77,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka really is a fast runner.
Dialogue: 6,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's usually pretty slow,
Dialogue: 6,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but sometimes she leaves us behind.
Dialogue: 6,0:11:13.81,0:11:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, Egawa and the others are going to eat it all.
Dialogue: 6,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 6,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:25.03,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.28\blur0.8\frz15.89\fscx145\fscy145\c&H2C0032&\1a&H55&\pos(983,273)}Saya Mart
Dialogue: 6,0:11:25.75,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I truly understand how much the people from Shioshishio helped out our store.
Dialogue: 6,0:11:32.65,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Produce and fish prices have gone up due to the weather, and they're staying there.
Dialogue: 6,0:11:37.01,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the world really is ending.
Dialogue: 6,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's tough it out, boss.
Dialogue: 6,0:11:42.02,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time to hit 'em with our best deals!
Dialogue: 6,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw, didn't you?
Dialogue: 6,0:11:54.62,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 6,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, get lost!
Dialogue: 6,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get lost somewhere, Aka{-chan}!
Dialogue: 6,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to get lost, you fake mom!
Dialogue: 6,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 6,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll upset Aka{-chan}, right?
Dialogue: 6,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll make her go back to the ocean, right?
Dialogue: 6,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll go to sleep, right?
Dialogue: 6,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't die, right?!
Dialogue: 6,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Miuna!
Dialogue: 6,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing this for her own good!
Dialogue: 6,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:35.94,How the Fuck Do I Typeset This,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\shad4\bord0\fax0.2\fscx131\fscy67\c&H714C8A&\4c&H000000&\4a&H56&\frz341.1\pos(1041,196)}G{\c&H3852A4&}e{\c&H3C6B43&}t
Dialogue: 6,0:12:27.75,0:12:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 6,0:12:29.19,0:12:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've already made up my mind.
Dialogue: 6,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Sakishima{-san}?
Dialogue: 6,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 6,0:12:37.99,0:12:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from the Fishery Cooperative Men's Club.
Dialogue: 6,0:12:41.06,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a request for your brother.
Dialogue: 6,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.62,Oshit Oshit; Fishy Business,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\frx0\fry342\fscx60\fscy60\c&HA7532F&\1a&H00&\pos(734,275)\org(723,454)}Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 6,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 6,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 6,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 6,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way we can get you guys to do the Boatdrift Ceremony?
Dialogue: 6,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about what happened at our last meeting.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We, uh...
Dialogue: 6,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,let our tempers get the better of us.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:11.52,0:13:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter right now.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing is:\N are you guys serious?
Dialogue: 6,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:18.10,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first told us about the winter,
Dialogue: 6,0:13:21.46,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we weren't really sure what to think.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the saltflake snow started falling, and the weather cooled down,
Dialogue: 6,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone realized it was real.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So please!
Dialogue: 6,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We beg of you!
Dialogue: 6,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Hikari...
Dialogue: 6,0:13:38.63,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,These people laughed at you in the past,
Dialogue: 6,0:13:42.44,0:13:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but now that fishing's declined and they can see what's happening,
Dialogue: 6,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,they want to work with you instead.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:48.25,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have every right to turn down such a self-centered request.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But if possible, please accept their plea.
Dialogue: 6,0:13:58.68,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The surface is a very important place to me.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone on the surface is gonna help us out, right?
Dialogue: 6,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. We'll do everything we can.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:18.65,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what we've decided as the Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 6,0:14:26.81,0:14:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 6,0:14:28.03,0:14:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone from the fishery cooperative said they'd help with the Boatdrift Ceremony!
Dialogue: 6,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well done, indeed.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:36.97,0:14:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However, even if you go through with the Boatdrift Ceremony, nothing will change.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 6,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 6,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what you said before!
Dialogue: 6,0:14:48.67,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I was just wondering if you could sway the feelings of the surface dwellers.
Dialogue: 6,0:14:55.60,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever say anything further would come of it?
Dialogue: 6,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 6,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the surface people!
Dialogue: 6,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Save them!
Dialogue: 6,0:15:12.05,0:15:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am but a scale of the sea god.
Dialogue: 6,0:15:15.80,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My powers cannot reach beyond the sea.
Dialogue: 6,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do about the surface.
Dialogue: 6,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 6,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}...
Dialogue: 6,0:15:35.31,0:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew all this yourself.
Dialogue: 6,0:15:37.86,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew that the Boatdrift Ceremony had no meaning or power.
Dialogue: 6,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 6,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently the humans weren't a total loss.
Dialogue: 6,0:15:49.89,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to tell them?!
Dialogue: 6,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We all worked so hard!
Dialogue: 6,0:15:56.41,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're still giving it\N their all as we speak.
Dialogue: 6,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 6,0:16:01.19,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know those guys must've hated \Nbowing their heads to a kid like me.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But they did it anyway.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:09.24,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said that we'd do whatever we could, and to leave it to me...
Dialogue: 6,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:16.15,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Everyone knows that.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Sis{Nee-chan}...
Dialogue: 6,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikari.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:24.31,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about something.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:36.88,0:16:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought them.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhand me!
Dialogue: 6,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a violation of human rights!
Dialogue: 6,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sue!
Dialogue: 6,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:50.63,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 6,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for gathering here today.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:54.82,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I'd like to ask of all of you.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all probably aware of this by now,
Dialogue: 6,0:17:00.96,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but Shiodome Itaru{-san} and I \Nare getting married.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 6,0:17:08.26,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if we could combine the Boatdrift Ceremony and wedding into one ceremony.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One ceremony?
Dialogue: 6,0:17:17.07,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you'd let me take the Wooden Maiden's place on the boat that drifts out to sea.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But does that mean...
Dialogue: 6,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be the sacrifice?
Dialogue: 6,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The maiden who calms the sea god's rage?
Dialogue: 6,0:17:31.39,0:17:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} said there was \Nno point to the Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:38.03,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure nothing will happen, just as {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} said.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There may well be no point in me doing this.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:45.11,0:17:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if there's nothing else we can do,
Dialogue: 6,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try everything we can just in case.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:53.45,0:17:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the Wooden Maiden.
Dialogue: 6,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the Boatdrift Ceremony is over,
Dialogue: 6,0:17:57.86,0:18:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll marry Itaru{-san}, just like the maiden married the sea god.
Dialogue: 6,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you... forgive me?
Dialogue: 6,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 6,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you go to sleep in the ocean,
Dialogue: 6,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you can keep living, right?
Dialogue: 6,0:18:13.85,0:18:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I want you to keep living, Aka{-chan}!
Dialogue: 6,0:18:18.11,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need you and Itaru{-san} in my life right now.
Dialogue: 6,0:18:24.71,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in me living without you two.
Dialogue: 6,0:18:28.69,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm sorry, but I'm never, ever
Dialogue: 6,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,going to get lost.{kinda awkward but shouganai}
Dialogue: 6,0:18:35.31,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to live my life in the same place and time as you, Miuna.
Dialogue: 6,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aka{-chan}!
Dialogue: 6,0:18:43.10,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 6,0:18:56.79,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if it's pointless.
Dialogue: 6,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to do something myself
Dialogue: 6,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,after seeing you all work so hard.
Dialogue: 6,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't want to say \Ngoodbye to all of you
Dialogue: 6,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,without doing everything I can!
Dialogue: 6,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 6,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a great idea!
Dialogue: 6,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 6,0:19:36.83,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take part too!
Dialogue: 6,0:19:38.33,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In the wedding!
Dialogue: 6,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 6,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 6,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just roll over and give up.
Dialogue: 6,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 6,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch, sea god!
Dialogue: 6,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put on a ceremony that not even you can ignore!
Dialogue: 6,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 6,0:20:01.51,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, the Boatdrift Ceremony was put into motion again.
Dialogue: 6,0:20:06.81,0:20:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like the very first one our ancestors held for the sea god.
Dialogue: 6,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the assistance of the fishery cooperative,
Dialogue: 6,0:20:20.43,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the fishermen started helping us out as well.
Dialogue: 6,0:20:25.01,0:20:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They let us use their shipyard,
Dialogue: 6,0:20:28.91,0:20:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the adults joined in to help us with our preparations.
Dialogue: 6,0:20:59.67,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 6,0:21:00.86,0:21:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you too!
Dialogue: 6,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 6,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 6,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari{-san}!
Dialogue: 6,0:21:10.38,0:21:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you check the fireplace and the door?
Dialogue: 6,0:21:20.33,0:21:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing. I really admire her.
Dialogue: 6,0:21:23.64,0:21:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's not just Akari{-san}.
Dialogue: 6,0:21:26.59,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari and Manaka are \Ntrying so hard to change.
Dialogue: 6,0:21:31.68,0:21:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only have they changed, but they're also changing everyone around them.
Dialogue: 6,0:21:36.07,0:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't let it remain unsaid.
Dialogue: 6,0:21:39.55,0:21:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Kaname has changed too.
Dialogue: 6,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari{-san}.
Dialogue: 6,0:21:44.67,0:21:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to confess my feelings to Hikari.{okada intensifies}
Dialogue: 6,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be futile,
Dialogue: 6,0:21:50.29,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't let it all end like this,\N everything unspoken.
Dialogue: 6,0:21:56.32,0:21:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I'm the same as the others.
