Dialogue: 6,0:23:31.07,0:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Manaka.
Dialogue: 6,0:23:32.84,0:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand any of that!
Dialogue: 6,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best that I can do.
Dialogue: 6,0:23:36.40,0:23:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 6,0:23:37.14,0:23:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget.
